{"word":"ἁρπακτός","slug":"ἁρπακτός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἁρπακτός</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἁρπάζω'><el>ἁρπάζω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>gotten by rapine, stolen</i>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to be caught</i>, <a href='S:id est'>i. e.</a> <i>to be got by chance, hazardous</i>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}